---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me | Console Craft"
	description="About Ovi Ispas, developer and founder of Console Craft"
>
	<section class="about">
		<div class="portrait-card">
			<img src="/images/people/ovi.jpg" alt="Portrait of Ovi Ispas" loading="lazy" />
		</div>

		<div class="about-copy">
			<p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
			<h1>Ovi Ispas</h1>
			<p>I'm a senior engineer / individual contributor who likes software that’s simple to use, flexible, and pleasantly boring in production.</p>
			<p>I spend most of my time in TypeScript, shipping modern web apps and developer CLI tools with a focus on reliability and maintainability.</p>
   <p>I love the brave new world of AI-powered development and tooling, especially AI coding agents, agentic engineering, and tools like OpenCode, while still being perfectly happy to drop into Neovim when a task calls for hands-on manual intervention.</p>
			<p>I publish indie projects under Console Craft: small utilities and apps designed to be genuinely useful, not just pet-projects. I'm a fan of the Unix philosophy, composability, and good defaults.</p>
			<div class="about-actions">
				<a class="action-button" href="https://github.com/console-craft" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Github</a>
				<a class="action-button" href="https://ro.linkedin.com/in/ovi-ispas" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(230px, 320px) minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
		align-items: start;
	}

	.portrait-card {
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 20px;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: var(--paper-strong);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
		animation: fade-up 760ms ease both;
	}

	.portrait-card img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
	}

	.about-copy {
		max-width: 42rem;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		font-size: 0.76rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--aqua);
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0.45rem 0 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--orange);
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	.about-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-top: 0.4rem;
	}

	.action-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		padding: 0.45rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		background: var(--accent-soft);
		color: var(--yellow);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.about {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.portrait-card {
			max-width: 340px;
		}
	}
</style>
